        "content": "<p>I was trying to implement(not prove) the Kruskal's algorithm using DSU <br>\nI found UnionFind in batteries<br>\nI am not sure how to evaluate the find function given an array and an index.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"sd\">/-- Find root of a union-find node, updating the structure using path compression. -/</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">find</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">UnionFind</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">self</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">UnionFind</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">×</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">//</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">self</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">self</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">findAux</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mf\">1.</span><span class=\"n\">arr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">s</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mf\">2.1</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">root</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mf\">1.</span><span class=\"n\">parentD_lt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Array</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">length_toList</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FindAux</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size_eq</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">parentD_findAux_lt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mf\">1.</span><span class=\"n\">rankD_lt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">rankD_findAux</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rankD_findAux</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">lt_rankD_findAux</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mf\">2.1</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">isLt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">show</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size_eq</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"mf\">2.2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">size</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">size_eq</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Below is how I evaluated the parentD function</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exampleUF</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Array</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Batteries</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">UFNode</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">Array</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Batteries</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">UnionFind</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">parentD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">UnionFind</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exampleUF</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- → 0</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Also how does it check whether the array i gave satisfies the properties of UFNode</p>",
